  <content contentuid="ha456196eg778egbbcag9f1cg6c78c15f9e9f" version="1">Bound to Nessus, the deepest layer of the Hells, these tieflings inherited the ability to wield fire and darkness from the archdevil Asmodeus' infernal bloodline.</content>
  <content contentuid="h3d865389g0f89gbb1eg7c79g19a210613730" version="1">Descended from devils of the Nine Hells, tieflings face constant suspicion in Faerûn. Thankfully, their arcane abilities make them natural survivors.</content>
