  <content contentuid="he3ba5549g2b0cgeb91g6d89g7a6986f0ec29" version="1">Creatures of intense emotion, half-orcs are more inclined to act than contemplate - whether the rage burning their bodies compels them to fight, or the love filling their hearts inspires acts of incredible kindness.</content>
