  <content contentuid="hc67be275g5942g31d7g30bfgbdb97352ae29" version="1">A proud race that values clan and skills above all else. Once enslaved by dragons, they strive to be self-sufficient, not wanting to be beholden to anyone, not even the gods.</content>
